headline: Assessing Keysight Technologies (KEYS) Valuation After SOS Enterprise AI Data Platform Launch
summary: Keysight Technologies (KEYS) just launched SOS Enterprise, an upgraded engineering data management platform that targets governance, traceability, and AI readiness across complex, multi-site design teams in sectors such as aerospace, defense, and automotive.
